#: src/kernel/index.md:1
msgid "Asterinas Kernel"
msgstr "Asterinas 内核"

#: src/kernel/index.md:3
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: src/kernel/index.md:5
msgid ""
"Asterinas is a _secure_, _fast_, and _general-purpose_ OS kernel that "
"provides an _Linux-compatible_ ABI. It can serve as a seamless replacement "
"for Linux while enhancing _memory safety_ and _developer friendliness_."
msgstr ""
"Asterinas 是一个**安全**、**快速**、**通用**的操作系统内核，提供**兼容 "
"Linux** 的 ABI。它能够无缝替代 Linux，同时增强**内存安全性**与**开发者友好性"
"**。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:10
msgid ""
"Asterinas prioritizes memory safety by employing Rust as its sole "
"programming language and limiting the use of _unsafe Rust_ to a clearly "
"defined and minimal Trusted Computing Base (TCB). This innovative approach, "
"known as [the framekernel architecture](the-framekernel-architecture.md), "
"establishes Asterinas as a more secure and dependable kernel option."
msgstr ""
"Asterinas 通过采用 Rust 作为唯一编程语言，并将 **unsafe Rust** 的使用限制在明"
"确界定且最小化的可信计算基（TCB）中，优先保障内存安全。这一被称为"
"[Framekernel 架构](the-framekernel-architecture.md)的创新方法，使 Asterinas "
"成为更安全可靠的内核选择。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:18
msgid ""
"Asterinas surpasses Linux in terms of developer friendliness. It empowers "
"kernel developers to (1) utilize the more productive Rust programming "
"language, (2) leverage a purpose-built toolkit called [OSDK]() to streamline "
"their workflows, and (3) choose between releasing their kernel modules as "
"open source or keeping them proprietary, thanks to the flexibility offered "
"by [MPL](../)."
msgstr ""
"Asterinas 在开发者友好性方面超越了 Linux。它使内核开发者能够：(1) 使用更高生"
"产力的 Rust 编程语言，(2) 借助名为 [OSDK]() 的专用工具包优化工作流程，以及 "
"(3) 得益于 [MPL](../) 提供的灵活性，自由选择将内核模块开源发布或保持专有。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:26
msgid ""
"While the journey towards a production-grade OS kernel can be challenging, "
"we are steadfastly progressing towards our goal. Currently, Asterinas only "
"supports x86-64 VMs. However, [our aim for 2024](roadmap.md) is to make "
"Asterinas production-ready on x86-64 for both bare-metal and VM environments."
msgstr ""
"虽然迈向生产级操作系统内核的旅程充满挑战，但我们正坚定地向目标推进。目前，"
"Asterinas 仅支持 x86-64 虚拟机。然而，[我们在 2024 年的目标](roadmap.md)是让 "
"Asterinas 在 x86-64 架构上，无论是裸机还是虚拟机环境，都能达到生产就绪状态。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:33
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "开始使用"

#: src/kernel/index.md:35
msgid ""
"Get yourself an x86-64 Linux machine with Docker installed. Follow the three "
"simple steps below to get Asterinas up and running."
msgstr ""
"准备一台安装了 Docker 的 x86-64 Linux 机器。按照以下三个简单步骤即可启动并运"
"行 Asterinas。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:38
msgid "Download the latest source code."
msgstr "下载最新源代码。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:44
msgid "Run a Docker container as the development environment."
msgstr "运行一个 Docker 容器作为开发环境。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:54
msgid ""
"Inside the container, go to the project folder to build and run Asterinas."
msgstr "在容器内，进入项目文件夹构建并运行 Asterinas。"

#: src/kernel/index.md:61
msgid "If everything goes well, Asterinas is now up and running inside a VM."
msgstr "如果一切顺利，Asterinas 现在应该已经在虚拟机中启动并运行了。"
